{"tid":573032,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"「惹火」J Law不停被罵　為性感造型企硬反駁網民","createTime":"2018-02-26T05:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T06:23:54.000Z","uid":40525,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"97a49cf58d523bb3941e1051f5018ac6b4fbdd6a","tid":573032,"uid":40525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T05:48:40.000Z","msg":"金像影后「J Law」珍妮花羅倫斯（Jennifer Lawrence）近期認真運滯，繼去年《媽媽！》備受劣評，全裸演出的新片《紅雀特工》亦被指抄襲，連早前自行放風聲，透露想息影一年投身政治活動，亦馬上被經理人公司反對，出聲明否認。但論矚目，必數幾日前她出席BAFTA頒獎禮時，被網民大罵她對國寶級主持Joanna Lumley無禮，更重提近幾年她失言的新聞，指大眾忍夠其壞脾氣云云。不過一向直言的珍妮花似乎未受影響，日前無懼三度低溫，以超性感晚裝出席新片宣傳，被罵口講支持女權，現實中卻甘願「物化」自己，性感示人。被罵多日的珍妮花似乎忍無可忍，在社交網站反駁網民，指自己有選擇權，穿那條裙全因漂亮，不願以大衣頸巾遮掩，火氣十足。眼見珍妮花到處辣着火頭，未知經理人公司會否順應其意，讓她息影<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2oqvRNs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2oqvRNs&d=RQ6dgMhbozDk5JWwv9bQ2DOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=d1666438\" target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2oqvRNs</a>"},{"pid":"0094ae7ccdc3a809f746040cd2ff340a446034fd","tid":573032,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T06:50:37.000Z","msg":"仲以為係Jude Law"},{"pid":"406ff0cec71e0ef95059699fc145f2c9f29e0966","tid":573032,"uid":27616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0094ae7ccdc3a809f746040cd2ff340a446034fd","tid":573032,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T06:50:37.000Z","msg":"仲以為係Jude Law"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T07:59:41.000Z","msg":"十年前就係"},{"pid":"57009ef2c0b9c30a913e7eccb21fdb0d4c1041e0","tid":573032,"uid":55043,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T08:01:05.000Z","msg":"女拳未傷到男人之前先傷女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606460946caa0a78db648fad399200e42a42d3ea","tid":573032,"uid":80724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T11:40:04.000Z","msg":"撐你啊J Law<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58a6ba3333dcaf0e